{"tid":761714,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"J2 刀劍神域劇場版 - 序列爭戰","createTime":"2018-07-30T15:19:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-30T15:19:57.000Z","uid":175335,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f4c33159c2dbc7b803a2f94fd3f392a2e06f7a08","tid":761714,"uid":175335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T15:19:57.000Z","msg":"尋晚J2 首播刀劍神域劇場版 - 序列爭戰 ，身為一名刀劍fans，捱夜都要睇！不過頭30秒已經令我黑人問號。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解介紹啲staff係英文字幕嚟嘅，我記得之前係戲院睇系日文嚟㗎喎？不過睇完都三點幾，瞓覺先，冇精力再深究。<br />\n今日睇返網上啲片，人地真係日文字幕嚟㗎喎<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/30/231852_4a47a0db6e60853dedfcfdf08a5ca249.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F30%2F231852_4a47a0db6e60853dedfcfdf08a5ca249.png&h=1e9f07e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/30/231856_fb5c81ed3a220004b71069645f112867.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F30%2F231856_fb5c81ed3a220004b71069645f112867.png&h=2a467c1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/30/231859_10fb15c77258a991b0028080a64fb42d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F30%2F231859_10fb15c77258a991b0028080a64fb42d.png&h=7caee53c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/30/231902_f19c9085129709ee14d013be869df69b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F30%2F231902_f19c9085129709ee14d013be869df69b.png&h=9cb633b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nTVB可能係買國際版嚟播啦<br />\n<br />\n同埋TVB啲翻譯真係麻麻<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/30/231922_09dd8c2662b96ce14928333f055c5580.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F30%2F231922_09dd8c2662b96ce14928333f055c5580.png&h=b6868900&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好似呢度咁，翻譯成 禁止通行 覺得好好多<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過最重要嘅亞絲娜出浴嗰度冇刪到，算係咁啦。"}]}